headline: Tractor Supply Makes Holiday Giving Easy, Affordable and Authentically "Out Here"
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 10, 2025--This holiday season, Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, is helping customers go the country mile with gifts that work as hard — and mean as much — as the people who live Life Out Here. From cozy comforts to tools built to last, the Tractor Supply 2025 Holiday Gift Guide is packed with ideas that make it easy to give practical, heartfelt gifts without overspending.
